translateItemList.eng: Artifacts are equipped to your General to grant Attack bonuses and special abilities. A General may have up to 3 artifacts equipped at once. Artifacts remain active until replaced or destroyed.
translateItemList.chi: 神器会使你的将领获得攻击加成和特殊效果。一个将领同时最多装备3件神器。神器在被摧毁后将会失效。

translateItemList.eng: Generals are powerful units that start the game on their respective side of the battlefield. Destroy the enemy general to win the game!
translateItemList.chi: 将领是游戏开始时就存在于战场上的强大单位，摧毁敌方将领来赢得战斗。

translateItemList.eng: Minions are units that may be played to the battlefield nearby another allied unit. Minions begin their first turn exhausted, but may move and attack at least once on each subsequent turn.
translateItemList.chi: 随从是可以在友军相邻位置被召唤的单位，在被召唤的第一回合将会进入力竭状态，在之后的回合里将可以至少移动和攻击1次。

translateItemList.eng: Spells are one-time effects that are activated when played.
translateItemList.chi: 法术在被使用时将会释放一次效果。
